<section class="rp-page-main">
  <div class="rp-shell">
    <div class="rp-page-main__grid">
      <div class="rp-page-main__content" data-rp-reveal>
        <p class="rp-section-eyebrow">Customer care</p>
        <h2 class="rp-section-heading">Support notes, made simple.</h2>
        <div class="rp-page-main__body rte">
          <p>Everything below covers the practical side of renting, from delivery timing and returns to fit guidance.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <aside class="rp-page-main__aside" data-rp-reveal>
        <div id="delivery-returns" class="rp-page-main__card">
          <p class="rp-page-main__card-label">Delivery &amp; returns</p>
          <p class="rp-page-main__card-copy">Your dress is sent using tracked Royal Mail delivery and timed around your booking window so it arrives ready for the moment.</p>
          <p class="rp-page-main__card-copy">On your return date, package the dress in the same box, take your parcel and QR code to your local post office, and let the team do the rest.</p>
          <p class="rp-page-main__card-copy">The item must be fully packed and dropped by 12pm on your return date. Late returns may incur additional charges.</p>
        </div>

        <div id="sizing" class="rp-page-main__card">
          <p class="rp-page-main__card-label">Sizing</p>
          <p class="rp-page-main__card-copy">Start with your usual occasionwear size and check each product page for any fit-specific notes.</p>
          <p class="rp-page-main__card-copy">If you are between sizes, prioritise comfort and movement, especially for longer events.</p>
          <p class="rp-page-main__card-copy">If your dress arrives and the fit is not right, contact us as soon as possible and we&rsquo;ll do our best to help.</p>
        </div>
      </aside>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "RP Support guides",
  "presets": [
    {
      "name": "RP Support guides"
    }
  ]
}
{% endschema %}
